Dear Stray kids, 
I don't think you'll ever read this, but I just want to tell you guys something. 
You always support us, and now , I, as a stay, support you. Always think of the good things. Enjoy your life, because it's short. There may be hard times, but never give up. I will always love you guys. You are the best. 
It's okay to show emotions, just don't be too sad. 
I hope that you guys will be okay and live a happy life. I will always listen to your music.
Your music makes me happy when I'm sad, and I hope you know that.
I love you.
